@sunsetsprite yes that is wonderful.  The more we see Dr. Ford, the more we remember. She can never become a footnote in history. Please repost if you like.  She is a hero. Thank you.

@shanawilsonartist your work is exceptional! I am incredibly moved by your capture of Dr. Ford. I hope it is ok, I am using your painting of Dr. Ford as my screen lock. A reminder of what courage is. Thank you.
@postapocalypticpeople just wondering if she was still your hero after she was never raped

Amazing portrait!! 👏 👏 She is a true American hero.
@angelapaul thank you. I really appreciate the support.  If you are interested in re-posting please go ahead. We can’t let Dr. Ford become just a footnote in history.  Best regards.
@kortney_olson thank you Kortney.  Dr. Ford is the incredible one. I’m just a painter. But I really appreciate your kind words. Thank you for all you do!
Where is she now with her $800,000 lump sum in a go fund me just suddenly disappeared. She wasn't even a doctor.
May I repost and credit you?

@travelinggringa thank you.  Dr. Ford is an amazing woman
